<Window
	xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
	xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
	xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008" xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006" mc:Ignorable="d"
	x:Class="WPFExpander.MainWindow"
	x:Name="Window"
	Title="WPF和Silverlight介绍"
	Width="640" Height="480" WindowStartupLocation="CenterScreen" Icon="picture/图3-3.jpg">

	<Grid x:Name="LayoutRoot">
		<Expander x:Name="expander1" Header="内容介绍" VerticalAlignment="Top" Expanded="expander1_Expanded" Collapsed="expander1_Collapsed" Cursor="Hand">
			<Grid x:Name="grid1" Background="#FFFFFDFD">
				<Grid.RowDefinitions>
					<RowDefinition Height="0.401*"/>
					<RowDefinition Height="0.599*"/>
				</Grid.RowDefinitions>
				<Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
					<ColumnDefinition/>
					<ColumnDefinition Width="Auto" MinWidth="277.2"/>
				</Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
				<Image x:Name="image" Grid.Column="1" Margin="-1.02,1,0,0.016"/>
				<RichTextBox x:Name="rtb1" Margin="0,1,1.02,0" VerticalScrollBarVisibility="Auto">
					<FlowDocument FontWeight="Medium">
						<Paragraph FontSize="14" FontFamily="宋体" Margin="0" TextAlignment="Justify" TextIndent="28"><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="计算机的操作系统是从单一文本界面发展起家的，乔布斯、比尔盖茨提出并发展了图像化的"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="Windows"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="，计算机界面的媒体形式丰富了，界面也漂亮了。随着网络技术的飞速发展，网络上的简单的文图界面也很快活跃起来，二维动画、三维动画、视频、流文档等多种媒体形式不断涌现，新技术层出不穷，“"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="RIA"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="”诞生了。"/></Span></Paragraph>
						<Paragraph FontSize="14" FontFamily="宋体" Margin="0" TextAlignment="Justify" TextIndent="28"><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="“"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="RIA"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="”（"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="Rich Internet Application"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="，富互联网应用），“"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="RIA"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="”同时具有丰富的媒体界面设计和丰富的数据交换设计功能，将会给下一代的项目应用设计带来指导性的影响，将会给用户带来一种新的设计体验。众多公司在“"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="RIA"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="”的开发方面做了很多工作。"/></Span></Paragraph>
						<Paragraph FontSize="14" FontFamily="宋体" Margin="0" TextAlignment="Justify" TextIndent="28"><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="大约"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="2002"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="年，"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="Macromedia"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="公司第一次提出“"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="RIA"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="”，并且在"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="2004"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="年推出了自己的“"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="RIA"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="”设计工具"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="Flex"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="。很快"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="Adobe"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="公司收购了"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="Macromedia"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="，并且不断升级"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="Flex"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="。"/></Span></Paragraph>
						<Paragraph FontSize="14" FontFamily="宋体" Margin="0" TextAlignment="Justify" TextIndent="28"><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run/></Span></Paragraph>
					</FlowDocument>
				</RichTextBox>
				<RichTextBox x:Name="rtb2" Margin="1.02,0,0,-2.98288333333335" VerticalScrollBarVisibility="Auto" Grid.Row="1" Grid.ColumnSpan="2">
					<FlowDocument FontStretch="Expanded">
						<Paragraph FontSize="14" FontFamily="宋体" Margin="0" TextAlignment="Justify" TextIndent="28"><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="微软公司不甘落后，在“"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="RIA"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="”的发展方面做了很多工作，推出了下一代操作系统、跨平台的设计软件。"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="2006"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="年微软发布了"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="Silverlight 1.0"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="（银色的光），这是一款基于网络应用设计软件，同时微软也推出基于桌面的富媒体设计软件"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="WPF"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="（"/></Span><Span Foreground="Black" Language="en-us"><Run Text="Windows Presentation Foundation"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="）。"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="2008"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="年，"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="Silverlight 2.0"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="在网络转播北京奥运会的设计中出了风头，引起众多“"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="RIA"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="”设计人员的关注。"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="2009"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="年"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="WPF 3.0"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="和"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="Silverlight 3.0"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="公布，"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="2010"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="又推出了第"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="4"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="版。"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="Visual Studio"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="是"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="WPF"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="和"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="Silverlight"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="的开发平台，为了用户设计方便，微软还同时推出了独立的开发平台"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="Expression Blend"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="，在这个开发环境中进行色彩设计、动画设计、"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="2D"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="和"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="3D"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="图形展示和界面交互设计显得非常方便，好似如虎添翼。"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="WPF"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="和"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="Silverlight"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="的后台开发语言是"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="C#"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="或"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="VB.NET"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="，这给"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="WPF"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="和"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="Silverlight"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="的开发和发展奠定了厚实基础。"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="WPF"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="和"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="Silverlight"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="是针对"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="XP"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="以上系统设计的，在"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="XP"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="下运行"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="WPF"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="应用需要添加"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text=".NET 3.0 Framework"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="以上环境，"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="Silverligh"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="应用需要在"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="IE"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="浏览器下安装"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="Silverlight"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="插件（可自动下载安装）。"/></Span></Paragraph>
						<Paragraph FontSize="14" FontFamily="宋体" Margin="0" TextAlignment="Justify" TextIndent="28"><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="从多媒体应用设计角度说，"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="WPF"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="和"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="Silverlight"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="比很多历史性软件，比如"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="Authorware"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="等，强大的多，操作也不复杂，先前的软件无法比拟。从数据处理的项目设计角度说，"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="WPF"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="和"/></Span><Span Language="en-us"><Run Text="Silverlight"/></Span><Span Language="zh-cn"><Run Text="同时有强大的多媒体表现和数据交换功能，给数据处理环境面目一新的体验。"/></Span></Paragraph>
						<Paragraph FontSize="14" FontFamily="宋体" Margin="0" TextAlignment="Justify" TextIndent="28"><Span Language="zh-cn"><InlineUIContainer>
									<Image x:Name="iamge1" Height="343" Source="picture/图3-3.jpg" Stretch="Fill" Width="556"/>
								</InlineUIContainer></Span></Paragraph>
					</FlowDocument>
				</RichTextBox>
				<Image x:Name="image2" Grid.Column="1" Margin="2.98,1,0,0.016" Source="picture/图3-3.jpg" Stretch="Fill"/>
			</Grid>
		</Expander>
		<Expander x:Name="expander2" Header="操作视频" ExpandDirection="Up" Margin="0,29.117,0,0" Expanded="expander2_Expanded" Collapsed="expander2_Collapsed" Cursor="Hand">
			<Grid x:Name="grid2" Background="#FFE5E5E5" Margin="0,0,0,5.98333333333334">
				<MediaElement x:Name="me" Stretch="Fill" LoadedBehavior="Manual" Source="picture/WPF操作2-画笔设置.wmv"/>
			</Grid>
		</Expander>
	</Grid>
</Window>